import React from 'react'
import NavBar from './components/NavBar'
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Switch, Route } from 'react-router-dom'

const App = () => {
  return (
        <Router>
          <NavBar></NavBar>
          <Switch>
            <Route path='/' exact />
          </Switch>
        </Router>
  )
}

export default App
